          </div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Nobody likes waiting for a slow website to load and your customers
            are no different. Research shows if your site takes longer than 3
            seconds to load, you risk losing more than half of your mobile
            visitors.
